title: 78. The Highs and Lows of the Self Love Journey
description:
Hey sis!

In this episode, we are talking all about the highs and lows of the self love journey and how it is ANYTHING but a linear, predictable process. We dive deep into balancing our humanness and our spirituality as we navigate codependency & our wounds.
